	hasOffenderID @A*(mm:prepend("O")), 
	hasName @B*,
	hasDateOfBirth @C*(xsd:dateTime mm:append("T00:00:00")),
	hasAge @D*(xsd:integer),
	hasNumberOfPreviousConvictions @E*(xsd:integer),
	hasMonthsSinceLastConviction @F*(xsd:integer),
	hasMonthsSinceLastImprisonment @G*(xsd:integer),
	hasResidentialStatus @H*,
	hasMonthsAtAddress @I*(xsd:integer),
	hasGangAffiliation @J*(xsd:boolean),
	hasEducationLevel @K*,
	hasEmployment @L*(xsd:boolean),
	hasNumberOfDependents @M*(xsd:integer),
	hasAlcoholDependent @N*(xsd:boolean),
	hasClassADrugDependent @O*(xsd:boolean),
	hasClassBDrugDependent @P*(xsd:boolean),
	hasGender @Q*,
	hasEthnicityCode @R*(mm:prepend("Eth-")),
	hasNationalityCode @S*(mm:prepend("Nat-")),
	hasMaritalStatusCode @T*(mm:prepend("MS-")),
	hasLSOAResidenceCode @U*(mm:prepend("LSOA-"))
